INSTALL: Build and Installation Instructions for FDF/FDFPP libraries.

== Prerequisites
   * CMake 2.8 or higher
   * C++ compiler
     - Microsoft Visual Studio 2010
     - gcc, g++ 4.0 or newer
     - clang/llvm 3.2 or newer
   * [Optional] Google testing framework, gtest-1.6.0 or higher.  Available
     from https://code.google.com/p/googletest/

== Building Linux/Mac OS X Command Line
   cmake . -DGTEST_DIR='/path/to/gtest/'
   make
[Optional] ./fdfpp_unittest1

== Building Windows Command Line
   cmake . -DGTEST_DIR='C:\Path\to\Gtest'
   msbuild fdfpp.sln -t:Build -p:Configuration=Release
[Optional] Release\fdfpp_unittst1.exe 


